-- HeidelbergCement Says Ludwig Merckle Increases Shareholding to Above 25%
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-11-05T11:16:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-05/heidelbergcement-says-ludwig-merckle-increases-shareholding-to-above-25-.html
HeidelbergCement AG said Ludwig
Merckle’s share of the company’s voting rights crossed the 25
percent threshold, and that he held 25.11 percent as of Nov. 4,
2010. A separate company statement cited Merckle as saying he
has no intention of obtining further voting rights “by
acquisition or by any other means” within the next 12 months.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
